('88ff7bd5-e64b-4603-98ec-5b2d4fd32136', 'progress', 'signed', '{"subjective":"MEDITECH REHAB NOTE — 55M, day 5 of inpatient rehabilitation following right hemispheric CVA. Left hemiparesis improving. Able to stand with moderate assist. Speech therapy working on mild neglect.","objective":"BP 138/82, HR 72. Neuro: Left UE 3/5 strength (↑ from 2/5 admission), Left LE 3+/5. FIM score: 62 (admission 45). Ambulating 50 feet with rolling walker and min assist. Tolerating regular diet with modified consistency liquids.","assessment":"Improving post-CVA. Making functional gains in PT/OT. Swallow function stable. Target FIM >80 for home discharge.","plan":"1. Continue PT/OT/ST 3 hours daily\n2. Continue secondary stroke prevention: ASA, statin, lisinopril\n3. INR monitoring for warfarin (if afib)\n4. Family training for home modifications\n5. Neuropsychology evaluation for cognitive rehab\n6. Estimated discharge in 7-10 days to home with home health"}', now() - interval '2 days');

